data.description:
Welcome to your dream home! Nestled within the highly sought-after Meridian neighborhood in Queen Creek, this immaculate 4-bedroom, 2-bathroom residence boasts over 2,500 square feet of luxurious living space and is ready to enchant you with its charm and elegance.

As you step through the front door, you will be greeted by a spacious and inviting floor plan adorned with tasteful finishes and an abundance of natural light. The open-concept living and dining areas seamlessly flow into the heart of the home, the gourmet kitchen. Perfectly appointed with granite countertops, stainless steel appliances, a large island with bar seating, and ample storage, this kitchen is a culinary enthusiast's dream. The generously sized primary bedroom offers a tranquil retreat featuring an en-suite bathroom with dual vanities, a soaking tub, a separate shower, and a walk-in closet. Three additional bedrooms provide plenty of space for family and guests. 

Step outside into your own private escape, where a beautifully landscaped backyard awaits. Whether you're looking to relax on the covered patio, enjoy a barbecue with friends and family, or play in the lush green grass, this outdoor space has it all. 

Additional highlights of this remarkable home include a convenient laundry room, an attached 2-car garage with epoxy floors & built-in cabinets. All at a location that provides easy access to shopping, dining, schools, and parks. 

Don't miss your opportunity to make this spectacular Meridian home your very own. It's the epitome of modern living in Queen Creek!
